data.name: Ablative Plate
data.description: The plate is tapered to absorb pulsed energy evenly. It intercepts about 9% of the bomb energy.

data.name: Ablative Nozzle
data.description: Thin layers of SiC are vaporized when struck by soft X-rays. Efficiency: 35%

data.name: De Laval Nozzle
data.description: In a nozzle, exhaust gases expand to supersonic speeds. Efficiency: 95% Expansion ratio: 100.
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 6 Rad-Hard De Laval Nozzle

data.name: Magnetic Nozzle
data.description: Magnetic fields contain plasmas hot enough to melt solid nozzles. Efficiency: 86%

data.name: Dumbo
data.description: Hydrogen coolant from a folded heat exchanger follows grooves in washer-shaped fuel elements. Power: 940 MWth Efficiency: 70%

data.name: Timberwind
data.description: The reactor is spun to form a fluidized bed of fuel grains swimming in H2 propellant. Power: 1880 MWth Efficiency: 71%

data.name: Hall Effect
data.description: 300 electrostatic thrusters. Thrust: 1.1 N each @ 2 ks. Total Power: 60 MWe Efficiency: 55%.

data.name: Ion Drive
data.description: 361 electrostatic thrusters. Thrust: 4 N each @ 8 ks. Total Power: 60 MWe Efficiency: 95%.

data.name: Mass Driver
data.description: A 390 m railgun launches buckets of dirt. Thrust: 7 kN @ 1.5 ks Energy: 7 GJ per shot Efficiency: 85%

data.name: MPDT-wave
data.description: Electromagnetic pulses eject propellant entrained by a superfluid. Frequency: 1 MHz. Efficiency: 81%

data.name: Metastable Helium
data.description: Helium in its metastable state stores 480 MJ/kg. Power: 260 MWth Efficiency: 72%

data.name: n-6Li Microfission
data.description: Exotic initiators permit propulsion by tiny nuclear bombs. Firing rate: 1/minute. Power: 3720 MWth Efficiency: 20%

data.name: Monatomic Plug Nozzle
data.description: Plug nozzle maximizing the recombination of monatomic hydrogen from a low pressure 3600 K reactor. Efficiency: 71%.
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 6 Rad-Hard Monatomic Plug Nozzle

data.name: Vortex Confined Nozzle
data.description: This reactor runs hot enough to vaporize the core, which is spun in a vortex. Power: 940 MWth Efficiency: 86%
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 7 Rad-Hard Vortex Confined Nozzle

data.name: Photon Heliogyro
data.description: A sail held rigid by centrifugal force. DeCom Immune to Flare & Belt Rolls. Max thrust @ 1 AU: 100 N
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 1 Rad-Hard Photon Heliogyro DeCom

data.name: Electric Sail
data.description: A positive electric field around thousands of tethers intercepts with the solar wind. DeCom Immune to Flare & Belt Rolls.
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 2 Rad-Hard Electric Sail DeCom

data.name: Photon Kite Sail
data.description: Sail driven by solar photons. DeCom Immune to Flare & Belt Rolls. Thrust @ 1 AU: 182 N (max), 69 N (useful)
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 0 Rad-Hard Photon Kite Sail DeCom

data.name: Mag Sail
data.description: Each Radiation Belt entered = Bonus Burn. Sail driven by solar wind protons. DeCom. Max thrust @ 1 AU: 110 N
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 4 Rad-Hard Mag Sail DeCom

data.name: Ponderomotive VASIMR
data.description: Variable Specific Impulse Magnetoplasma Rocket with 15 electrothermal thrusters. Total Power: 60 MWe Efficiency: 72%

data.name: Pulsed Plasmoid
data.description: A powersat laser beam initiates ball-lightning plasmoids. Power: 60 MWe Efficiency: 72%

data.name: Pulsed Inductive
data.description: 75 PIT thrusters. Thrust: 60 N each. Total Power: 60 MWe Efficiency: 72%. Propellant: H2O.

data.name: Dual-Stage 4-Grid
data.description: Ion drive with 4 grids. Total Thrust: 1.1 kN @ 11.2 ks Total Power: 60 MWe Efficiency: 98%

data.name: Re Solar Moth
data.description: Hydrogen is remotely heated to 5800 K Nozzle: 26 kN @ 1 ks Power: 15 MWth Efficiency: 87%
data.rawText: Thruster 0 MASS 5 Rad-Hard Re Solar Moth

data.name: Colliding Beam H-B Fusion
data.description: Beams of hydrogen and boron are injected via a field-reversed plasma. Power: 1500 MWth Efficiency: 83%
data.rawText: Thruster 2 MASS 5 Rad-Hard Colliding Beam H-B Fusion
